---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About | Julio Cesar">
  <main>
    <h1>About me</h1>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        I'm a Data Engineer at an insurance company in Panama, where I work with 
        large-scale data processing using Databricks, PySpark, dbt, and MLflow.
      </p>
      <p>
        I handle datasets of over 15 terabytes and more than a billion records, 
        focusing on insurance analytics, premium calculations, and machine learning 
        model development.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have a background in Physics and experience in full-stack development and teaching.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Research Interests</h2>
      <p>
        With my physics background, I'm deeply interested in exploring the intersection 
        of Quantum Computing and Artificial Intelligence. I'm fascinated by how quantum 
        algorithms could revolutionize machine learning and optimization problems â€” 
        areas where I already work daily with classical approaches.
      </p>

      <h2>Technologies</h2>
      <div class="tags">
        <span>Databricks</span>
        <span>PySpark</span>
        <span>dbt</span>
        <span>MLflow</span>
        <span>Python</span>
        <span>SQL</span>
        <span>Delta Lake</span>
      </div>

      <h2>Interests</h2>
      <div class="tags interests">
        <span>Quantum Computing</span>
        <span>Artificial Intelligence</span>
        <span>Machine Learning</span>
        <span>Data Architecture</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  main {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #111827;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  p {
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .tags span {
    background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .tags.interests span {
    background: linear-gradient(14deg, #d83333 0%, #f041ff 100%);
  }
</style>